04:26.690 --> 04:30.292
<i>♪ See the money,</i>
<i>wanna stay for your meal ♪</i>

04:30.327 --> 04:33.595
<i>♪ Get another piece of pie</i>
<i>for your wife ♪</i>

04:33.631 --> 04:36.732
<i>♪ Everybody wanna know</i>
<i>how it feel ♪</i>

04:36.767 --> 04:40.435
<i>♪ Everybody wanna see</i>
<i>what it's like ♪</i>

04:40.471 --> 04:43.305
<i>♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,</i>
<i>I don't mind ♪</i>

04:43.340 --> 04:47.242
<i>♪ Me and Missy is</i>
<i>so busy, busy making money ♪</i>

04:47.278 --> 04:48.710
<i>♪ All right ♪</i>

04:48.746 --> 04:49.016
<i>♪ All step back,</i>
<i>I'm 'bout to dance ♪</i>

04:49.017 --> 04:54.217
